273
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:54,080
Seharusnya Li Qian juga
sudah tiba di pos istirahat ini, 'kan?

274
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:58,320
Kurasa gadis itu juga ikut kemari.

275
00:16:59,880 --> 00:17:00,559
Abaikan saja dia.

276
00:17:08,319 --> 00:17:09,000
Li Qian?

277
00:17:09,959 --> 00:17:10,719
Tak mungkin, 'kan?

278
00:17:26,760 --> 00:17:27,880
Benar-benar kau?

279
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:31,199
Ke... Kenapa kau ada di sini?

280
00:17:31,439 --> 00:17:33,280
Seharusnya aku yang tanya
pada Putri Agung.

281
00:17:33,900 --> 00:17:36,380
Kau tak perlu rayakan ulang tahun
Ibu Suri di Gunung Wanshou.

282
00:17:36,380 --> 00:17:37,160
Kenapa kau kemari?

283
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:42,720
Apa mungkin kau cemas Ibu Suri
takkan percaya saat Keluarga Li...

284
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:43,839
