memberimu pelajaran!

376
00:22:31,520 --> 00:22:34,920
Terima kasih atas kebaikan Kaisar!

377
00:22:40,199 --> 00:22:43,040
Salam kepada Putri Agung.

378
00:22:50,800 --> 00:22:51,520
Putri Agung.

379
00:22:52,760 --> 00:22:54,800
Aku sudah bersalah tadi.

